# Three-Address Code (TAC) - Optimized

 1: DECL float globalX
 2: FUNC_BEGIN Master
 3: DECL float x
 4: DECL int y
 5: DECL bool s
 6: s = 1
 7: x = 10
 8: y = 20
 9: DECL char c
10: c = 103
11: DECL float z
12: z = t3
13: PRINT t3
14: x = t4
15: PRINT t4
16: PRINT 20
17: PRINT 1
18: t5 = 103 + t4
19: PRINT t5
20: globalX = t4
21: RETURN
22: FUNC_END Master
